# A collection of 7210 Doodmas Delights
Doodmas Delights takes a Christmas spin on byburnttoast‚Äôs Doodles collection!  
10 of 1/1s will be on auction, others will be minted for free!  
The collection consists of 7,210 unique, non-fungible tokens (NFTs) on the Ethereum blockchain.  
There exist 135 hand-drawn traits, with unique generative algorithms created for each base Doodmas and 20 purely hand-drawn Doodmas‚Äô.  
Our goal is to spread the gift-giving spirit, and to educate our friends and family about NFTs and the space that we love! We believe that Doodmas Delights can play a role in spreading Doodles, and the NFT space as a whole, across the mainstream into popular adoption.

data.name: Dreams of EVM
data.description:
Explore the EVM with dreams

The EVM‚Äôs physical instantiation can‚Äôt be described in the same way that one might point to a cloud or an ocean wave, but it does exist as one single entity maintained by thousands of connected computers running an Ethereum client.

The Ethereum protocol itself exists solely for the purpose of keeping the continuous, uninterrupted, and immutable operation of this special state machine; It's the environment in which all Ethereum accounts and smart contracts live. At any given block in the chain, Ethereum has one and only one 'canonical' state, and the EVM is what defines the rules for computing a new valid state from block to block.

data.name: DRIVE // BY DAVE KRUGMAN
data.description:
DRIVE is an NFT Photography Collection from Dave Krugman, featuring 111 1/1 vehicles, aggregated over the course of ten years of street photography. But this project is more than just a collection- it is an ecosystem of access, a dynamic community game, and an entry ticket to a wide range of future endeavors.

Minted on a @manifoldxyz contract, DRIVE is broken down into the following categories.

There are 20 Trophies, representing the most rarefied visuals. Aliens, classic restorations, and strange designs abound. To win a Trophy, you must own a car, and enter it into a race event.

There will be various race events and mechanics, gamified via social media. 

There are 8 Grails up for a 24 HR Auction. 

Tier 1- 25 cars at .5 ETH
Tier 2- 33 cars at .33 ETH
Tier 3- 25 cars at .25 ETH

There are a lot of visual rarities spread throughout ALL Tiers of the collections. Some cars have qualities that are entirely unique. I won‚Äôt spoil those secrets, it is up to the community to determine.

The very first NFT artworks by Alejandro and Taylor. 

These early works were minted for 0.02 eth each back before Alejandro and Taylor released their first collections (https://opensea.io/collection/mirage-gallery). 

Alejandro and Taylor each released 5 pieces and there were able to be 100 copies of each. But the minting ended early since they didn't all mint in time.
